dc_title_s: Dernières explorations en Asie et dans les régions polaires 1880; dessinée par J. Hansen.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. Names of explorers are in red. Shows the routes of explorers in the Arctic region and Asia. 1 map: col.; 26 x 26 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
